    <updated>2019-11-26T14:10:17.000Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>#由于WordPress官方网站wordpress.org的CDN服务器屏蔽了大陆ip,导致后#台WordPress和程序无法更新.<br>#为此我通过网络代理和服务器命令更新了插件和主程序，命令流记录如下</p><h3 id="1-ssr"><a href="#1-ssr" class="headerlink" title="1.ssr"></a>1.ssr</h3><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git clone https://github.com/ssrbackup/shadowsocksr</span><br><span class="line">sudo cp shadowsocksr/config.json /etc/shadowsocks.json</span><br><span class="line">sudo vim /etc/shadowsocks.json</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash"><span class="comment">#ssr代理通过网络搜索获得，并验证可用</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash"><span class="comment">##配置文件如下格式</span></span></span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    "local_address": "127.0.0.1",</span><br><span class="line">    "local_port": 1080,</span><br><span class="line">    "enable": true,</span><br><span class="line">    "method": "aes-256-cfb",</span><br><span class="line">    "obfs": "plain",</span><br><span class="line">    "obfsparam": "",</span><br><span class="line">    "password": "bTuK5IJr9hzl",</span><br><span class="line">    "protocol": "origin",</span><br><span class="line">    "protocolparam": "",</span><br><span class="line">    "remarks_base64": "IzdFMUQvQVMzNDYyOiBUYWl3YW4",</span><br><span class="line">    "server": "*.*.*.*",</span><br><span class="line">    "server_port": 21971</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash"><span class="comment">##启动代理</span></span></span><br><span class="line">sudo python shadowsocksr/shadowsocksr/local.py -c /etc/shadowsocks.json -d start</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash"><span class="comment">### ssr代理资源比较多，但是无法在终端直接使用socks5代理,为此需要安装proxychains</span></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="2-proxychains"><a href="#2-proxychains" class="headerlink" title="2. proxychains"></a>2. proxychains</h3><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git clone https://github.com/rofl0r/proxychains-ng.git</span><br><span class="line">cd proxychains-ng</span><br><span class="line">./configure --prefix=/usr --sysconfdir=/etc</span><br><span class="line">sudo make</span><br><span class="line">sudo make install</span><br><span class="line">sudo vim /etc/proxychains.conf</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash"><span class="comment">##修改最后一行，启用ssr的sock5代理</span></span></span><br><span class="line">socks5  127.0.0.1 1080</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="3-wp-cl"><a href="#3-wp-cl" class="headerlink" title="3. wp-cl"></a>3. wp-cl</h3><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">wget https://raw.github.com/wp-cli/builds/gh-pages/phar/wp-cli.phar</span><br><span class="line">chmod +x wp-cli.phar </span><br><span class="line">sudo cp wp-cli.phar /usr/bin/wp</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash"><span class="comment">##创建缓存文件夹，修改缓存文件夹权限</span></span></span><br><span class="line">sudo mkdir -p /home/www/.wp-cli/cache/</span><br><span class="line">sudo chown -R www:www /home/www</span><br><span class="line">sudo chmod -R 777 /home/www/.wp-cli/</span><br><span class="line">sudo su</span><br><span class="line">export WEBPATH=/www/wwwroot/liuqh.phy.sustech.edu.cn</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash"><span class="comment">##检查需要更新的插件</span></span></span><br><span class="line">sudo -u www -- wp plugin list --path=$WEBPATH</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash"><span class="comment">##依次更新插件</span></span></span><br><span class="line">for i in all-in-one-wp-migration all-in-one-seo-pack http-headers;do proxychains4 sudo -u www -- wp plugin update $i --path=$WEBPATH;done</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash"><span class="comment">##更新主程序和数据库</span></span></span><br><span class="line">proxychains4 sudo -u www -- wp core update  --path=$WEBPATH</span><br><span class="line">proxychains4 sudo -u www -- wp core update-db  --path=$WEBPATH</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
